Why this file exists
---------------------
This repository was created by manually cloning the upstream source and
reinitializing git history, rather than using GitHub's "Fork" feature,
because forking was blocked by the upstream maintainer. As a result, the
commit history, authorship metadata, and contributor attribution that a
native GitHub fork would normally preserve are not present in this
repository's git log. This file exists to preserve that attribution, as
required by Section 4(c) of the Apache License 2.0.

